{"tid":265014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人知呢條友而家係咪仲揸緊巴士？","createTime":"2017-05-31T10:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T10:25:09.000Z","uid":18105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55155324944465b2fea3804d6f994bed73a2a796","tid":265014,"uid":18105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:11:13.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】追夢有很多方式，有人放棄高薪厚職去做義工；有人孭着背包遠走天涯。現年26歲曾是會考9A狀元、早前還是金融才俊的阿彥，卻為實現兒時夢想，辭去會計師樓經理之職，脫下西裝解下領帶，穿上制服揸巴士，他說：「錢幾時都搵到，但夢想唔係幾時都可以實現。」手握巴士軚盤的阿彥笑說。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20130520/18265592\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20130520%2F18265592&d=UKJ7iNP0vuxfX4FTDXyrgf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=5f1a65d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20130520%2F18265592&h=99a572fa\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20130520/18265592</a>"},{"pid":"85244a361d27599df7a457d4e59562ecb67e34ac","tid":265014,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:13:16.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n不過做寫字樓多"},{"pid":"ff598197e47719bad5bd6be6fe21e3386c658478","tid":265014,"uid":25641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:14:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a2d996165f818aacbcd2b928f83e4109e8e1c76","tid":265014,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我作文成日寫佢"},{"pid":"d9f629a2e09511e8915695bca0e05290eaec0ba5","tid":265014,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:16:14.000Z","msg":"上左寫字樓"},{"pid":"b91c34dcd5783b720a850321501dc518477ff5fe","tid":265014,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:17:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我作文成日寫佢</blockquote><br /